name: All Over The World The Spirit Is Moving
chorusText:
All over the world
(C)

* All over the world, the Spirit is moving
All over the world, as the prophets said it would be
All over the world, there’s a mighty revelation
of the Glory of the Lord
as the waters covered the sea.

* Deep down in my heart, the Spirit is moving

* Right here in this place, the Spirit is moving
